<br />
Your pet inherits your resists <span style="font-style: italic">at the time of summoning</span>. They'll keep those same resists throughout the time they're up, regardless of what spells drop on you, or what buffs you get <span style="font-style: italic">after</span> summoning them.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">
